SOLARIS-NOTIFICATION TESTS
-----------
Tests that verify "Solaris Pop-up Notifications" functionality.

Safety
------
These tests will not change anything in system, they are safe to run.

Configuration
-------------
No configuration is needed

Version
-------
Tests were updated for Solaris11 and its update release

Available Testsuites
--------------------
* Set pop-up notification dialog to Bottom Right position and preview it
* Set pop-up notification dialog to Bottom Left position and preview it
* Set pop-up notification dialog to Top Right position and preview it
* Set pop-up notification dialog to Top Left position and preview it
* Set pop-up notification dialog to Bottom Right position and preview it
